      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_B49BA760-1EEC-0135-E93F-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Start to type a name in the text field [1], or click the <strong>Address Book</strong> icon [2] to filter by users or course groups.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="use_address_book" data-step-uuid="455f48f0-e253-40ac-80dc-1519e9940bf1">
    <h3 id="use_address_book" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Use Address Book</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/636/490/original/fd468eb4-b051-4770-b205-f47ac5d7ba78.png" srcset="" alt="Use Address Book" height="297" width="768">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_B49BD920-1EEC-0135-E941-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the individual and select his or her name [1]. Names are sorted by last name.</p>
<p>To navigate back to the address book, click the <strong>Address Book</strong> button [2].</p>
<p>To exit the course roster menu, press <strong>Return</strong> (on a MAC keyboard) or <strong>Enter</strong> (on a PC keyboard).</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

